282
00:30:12,725 --> 00:30:15,352
<font color=#FFFF00>Era minha escolha.</font>

283
00:30:15,353 --> 00:30:17,980
<font color=#FFFF00>E tirou isso de mim, Dale.</font>

284
00:30:17,981 --> 00:30:22,609
<font color=#FFFF00>- Mas...
