295
00:30:53,975 --> 00:30:58,975
<font color=#FFFF00>Só há isso a dizer.</font>

296
00:31:17,999 --> 00:31:19,666
<font color=#FFFF00>Shane, veja.</font>

297
00:31:19,667 --> 00:31:22,044
<font color=#FFFF00>Papai disse que poderia levar
